      <h2>Contribute</h2>

      <p><a href="http://badgr.co/">Badgr.co</a> is written in Python using <a
      href="http://aspen.io/">Aspen</a> and is in the public domain.</p>

      <pre>$ git clone git@github.com:gittip/badgr.co.git
$ cd badgr.co
$ make run</pre>

      <p>Dependencies are included in the <a
        href="https://github.com/gittip/badgr.co/tree/master/vendor">vendor</a>
      directory.</p>

      <p>Look at <a
      href="https://github.com/gittip/badgr.co/blob/master/badgr/services.py">badgr/services.py</a>
      to add a new service.</p>


